{"tid":2341570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界所有野，係你嘅就係你嘅","createTime":"2020-12-26T13:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T13:47:01.000Z","uid":89520,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75dc85f5ef639656ccf281cb64ef48e6e56a0a4e","tid":2341570,"uid":89520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"頭先pack返d野同寫咗封信拎去佢屋企比佢，喺Ex門口等咗好耐，佢呀爸終於出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n同我講咗一句，「唉，呢個世界係你嘅就係你架啦，等一段時間先啦仔」<br />\n<br />\n咁大個仔未試過一路揸車一路喊，眼淚不自覺地一滴一滴滴落軚盤，前面嘅路我已經睇唔清。<br />\n<br />\n不過我同自己講，有一日一定會追返佢返嚟"},{"pid":"791120dcac9927493805127f0d0087fa3587a3f9","tid":2341570,"uid":241596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c20a03da5b405466457e6fec1dce300ba088d6","tid":2341570,"uid":108690,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"最難得係人地老豆安慰你 証明你已經過左佢老豆個關<br />\n<br />\n雖然你唔係同佢老豆拍拖"},{"pid":"aa3aa7f74f8133a23d3633afaa387fcedc72a63d","tid":2341570,"uid":89520,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96c20a03da5b405466457e6fec1dce300ba088d6","tid":2341570,"uid":108690,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"最難得係人地老豆安慰你 証明你已經過左佢老豆個關<br />\n<br />\n雖然你唔係同佢老豆拍拖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:23:52.000Z","msg":"唉但我衰多口，講咗句，佢無第二個架可，其實好唔respect佢"},{"pid":"b416435f70cf0efefb5602b5285c70c39efff97b","tid":2341570,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"嘻 傻仔"},{"pid":"fa46d25eacdecf0c615db3f81875d89c8dc9b17e","tid":2341570,"uid":89520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b416435f70cf0efefb5602b5285c70c39efff97b","tid":2341570,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"嘻 傻仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"當試驗下自己究竟有幾鍾意同在意佢"},{"pid":"d728adb8e287f9f2572623